     <div type="epigraph">
   <pb n="92" facs="58"/>
   <head>
      <hi>TO</hi> All Good Husbands.</head>
   <l>Good Husbands all, receaue in thank<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>full part,</l>
   <l>This Sacrifice, (which may my Will approue:)</l>
   <l>Upon the Altar of a faythfull Heart,</l>
   <l>Consumed in the Flames of Zeale an<gap reason="illegible" resp="#oxf" extent="1 letter">
         <desc>•</desc>
      </gap> Loue.</l>
   <l>Let Honourable Woman liue for ever,</l>
   <l>In all that Arte, that Tyme, that Fame can giue <hi>hER.</hi>
   </l>
</div>
